      "section": [
        "Whale's tooth scimitar"
      ],
      "text": "The whale's tooth scimitar is a Water Tribe weapon made by attaching the tooth of a whale to the end of a long, wooden stick. Although it may appear primitive, the scimitar can actually be deadly. Its small, mobile size is practical for close-range combat. The whale's tooth scimitar was used by warriors from both the Southern and Northern Water Tribes during the Hundred Year War."
    },
    {
